Crucially, while CG-nAR (Paper 5) uses concepts, it does not perform *hierarchical conceptual reasoning* or *dynamic gating of model components*. DCG thus represents a more substantial leap in both mechanism and autonomy, offering a new paradigm for adaptive, efficient inference grounded in emergent semantics rather than fixed rules.

